title: JUDD APATOW IN CONVERSATION WITH RONNY CHIENG (SPONSORED)
description: The legendary director, producer, and comedic genius behind such classics as Freaks & Geeks, Bridesmaids, and Knocked Up offers a rare glimpse behind the curtain with stories about our favorite comedians and his beloved films. Join us for what promises to be a rollicking night celebrating the biggest comedy nerd in show biz and his storied journey to Hollywood superstardom. In conversation with Ronny Chieng (The Daily Show).
